description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Flow - Day 20 - Inward' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Day 20. This is huge. You made it to Day 20! And perfectly timed, we take this session to continue the journey inward. This session asks a lot of good questions and continues to cultivate and add new vocabulary to the physical practice. This is time well spent with yourself.
